      "rdf:value": "<L>144913<pc>730,2<k1>bAhu<k2>bAhu/<h>1<e>1\r\n<hom>1.</hom> <s>bAhu/</s> ¦ <lex>m.</lex> <lex>f.</lex> (<lex type=\"hwinfo\">f.</lex>, <ls>L.</ls>) (<ab>fr.</ab> √ <s>bah</s>, <s>baMh</s>; for <hom>2.</hom> <s>bAhu</s> See <ab>col.</ab> 3) the arm, (<ab>esp.</ab>) the forearm, the arm between the elbow and the wrist (<ab>opp.</ab> to <s>pra-gaRqa</s>, <ab>q.v.</ab>; in <ab>medic.</ab> the whole upper extremity of the body, as <ab>opp.</ab> to <s>sakTi</s>, the lower <ab n=\"extremity\">ext˚</ab>), <ls>RV.</ls> &c. &c.<info lex=\"m:f\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
