      "rdf:value": "<L>76884<pc>4-223-b<k1>bAhu<k2>bAhu/\n{#bAhu/#}¦\n<div n=\"1\">— 1〉 <lex>m.</lex> (*<lex>f.</lex>)\n<div n=\"2\">— a〉 {%Arm,%} in engerer <ab>Bed.</ab> {%Vorderam;%} in der Medicin {%die ganze obere Extremität%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— b〉 als {%Längenmaass%} = 12 <is>Aṅgula</is> <ls>ŚULBAS. 1,14</ls>.\n<div n=\"2\">— c〉 beim Thier {%Vorderfuss,%} <ab>insbes.</ab> {%der obere Theil desselben%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— d〉 {%Arm des Bogens%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— e〉 {%Arm der Wagendeichsel%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— f〉 {%Pfosten%} einer Thür.\n<div n=\"2\">— g〉 {%Seite einer geometrischen Figur,%} <ab>insbes.</ab> {%Kathete%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— h〉 {%the sine of an are of a circle of position contained between the Sun and the Prime Vertical%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— i〉 {%der Schatten eines Sonnenzeigers%}.\n<div n=\"2\">— k〉 <ab>Sg.</ab> und <ab>Pl.</ab> {%das Mondhaus%} <is>Ārdrā</is>.\n<div n=\"1\">— 2〉 <lex>m.</lex> <ab>N. pr.</ab> eines <is>Daitya</is>.\n<div n=\"2\">— b〉 verschiedener Fürsten.\n<LEND>"
